===================================
Solving Systems of Linear Equations                               [TOC]
===================================

Compare this example with __flens/examples/lapack-gesv__.

Like in __flens/examples/lapack-gesv__ we solve a system of linear equations
$Ax = b.$  But instead of using the driver function __lapack::sv__ we first
compute the $LU$ factorization of $A$ with __lapack::trf__ and then use the
triangular solver __blas::sm__ to finish the job.  So basicaly we do manually
what __lapack::sv__ does internally.

:links:  __lapack::sv__  -> file:flens/lapack/gesv/sv.h
         __lapack::trf__ -> file:flens/lapack/gesv/trf.h
         __blas::sm__    -> file:flens/blas/level3/sm.h
         __(.+)__        -> doc:$1


